                            <div class="flip-back" style="border-color:var(--goku-primary);"><strong>The Physical Look</strong><br><br>The physical, visible expression of the trait caused by the genes.<br><br><strong>Example:</strong> <span class="exam-keyword">Tall</span> or <span class="exam-keyword">Short</span></div>
