        <div class="slide">
            <div class="content-box">
                <h2>1. Ecosystems & Energy Flow</h2>
                <p>Ecosystems rely on a <strong>unidirectional</strong> flow of energy. Plants (Producers) capture about 1% of the sun's energy to make food.</p>
                <div style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 5px solid var(--goku-primary); margin-top: 15px;">
                    <h3>The 10% Law <span class="punjabi">(10% ਦਾ ਨਿਯਮ)</span></h3>
                    <p>Only <span class="exam-keyword">10%</span> of energy is transferred from one trophic level to the next. The other 90% is lost as heat. Because so much energy is lost, food chains rarely go beyond 3 or 4 steps!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FIXED SLIDE 61: Intuitive Sequencer for Biomagnification -->
        <div class="slide">
